            <rect x="17.9219" y="0.00012207" width="8.96048" height="8.96048" fill="#3A3737"/>
            <rect x="8.95996" y="8.96033" width="8.96048" height="8.96048" fill="#3A3737"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-10 sm:mt-16 lg:mt-18 font-display text-[1.625rem] md:text-4xl lg:text-[2.5rem] xl:text-[3.5rem] leading-[1.2] uppercase">
          <p>Le design attire, <br class="lg:hidden">l’expérience retient.</p>
          <p>Nous créons des interfaces intuitives qui répondent aux intentions de vos utilisateurs.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <Physics class='mt-10 sm:mt-16 lg:mt-18 xl:mt-24' />
